### ============================================================================
### DrasiLib Dashboard Example - REST Client
### ============================================================================
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools.
###
### HTTP Source: POST http://localhost:9000/sources/stock-prices/events
### Dashboard:  http://localhost:3000
### ============================================================================

### Health check
GET http://localhost:9000/health

###

### ============================================================================
### INSERT OPERATIONS
### ============================================================================

### Insert a new stock (AMD)
POST http://localhost:9000/sources/stock-prices/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operation": "insert",
  "element": {
    "type": "node",
    "id": "price_AMD",
    "labels": ["stock_prices"],
    "properties": {
      "symbol": "AMD",
      "price": 165.50,
      "previous_close": 160.00,
      "volume": 3200000
    }
  }
}

###

### ============================================================================
### UPDATE OPERATIONS
### ============================================================================

### AAPL price increase — will appear in gainers
POST http://localhost:9000/sources/stock-prices/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operation": "update",
  "element": {
    "type": "node",
    "id": "price_AAPL",
    "labels": ["stock_prices"],
    "properties": {
      "symbol": "AAPL",
      "price": 182.00,
      "previous_close": 173.00,
      "volume": 7500000
    }
  }
}

